OL,3,CMan travels to France for surgery to
OL,4,Cavoid long wait times
OL,6,FA man has travelled to to get a double
OL,7,Fknee replacement after becoming
OL,8,Ffrustrated with wait times and the
OL,9,Fcost of the operation on island.
OL,11,FJonathan Travers joined the surgery
OL,12,Flist in 2022 and says he was left
OL,13,Funable to work for the last 18 months
OL,14,Fas he dealt with "non-stop pain".
OL,16,FHe told ITV News that on hearing it
OL,17,Fcould take two years or more before
OL,18,Fgetting his knees replaced, he
OL,19,Ftravelled to France in January 2024 to
OL,20,Fhave the operation carried out there
OL,21,Finstead.
