OL,3,CMan travels to France for surgery to
OL,4,Cavoid long wait times
OL,6,FThe difference in medical bills was
OL,7,Falso stark with Jonathan quoted
OL,8,F#14,500 per knee for private treatment
OL,9,Fin Guernsey - it cost #8,500 to have
OL,10,Fboth done in France.
OL,12,FJonathan says the difference since
OL,13,Fsurgery is "absolutely phenomenal".
OL,15,FHe added: "My grandson is four and I
OL,16,Fcould not keep up with him, but now I
OL,17,Fcan. My granddaughter isn't walking
OL,18,Fyet, but now I can carry them."
