OL,3,CMan travels to France for surgery to
OL,4,Cavoid long wait times
OL,6,FWaiting lists remain stubborn in
OL,7,FGuernsey, averaging around 800, but
OL,8,Fthe opening of the dedicated De
OL,9,FHavilland Ward has helped to reduce
OL,10,Ftimes in orthopaedics.
OL,12,FThe unit carried out 453 major joint
OL,13,Freplacements in 2023 - although there
OL,14,Fare still concerns over the
OL,15,Frecruitment of staff and an ageing
OL,16,Fpopulation that is likely to put more
OL,17,Fpressure on services.
