OL,3,CMan travels to France for surgery to
OL,4,Cavoid long wait times
OL,6,FDeputy Al Brouard, President of
OL,7,FGuernsey's Health & Social Care
OL,8,FCommittee, explained: "The need for
OL,9,Fmore nurses is one issue and of
OL,10,Fcourse, we've been trying to get
OL,11,Fnursing accommodation on the Princess
OL,12,FElizabeth Hospital site.
OL,14,F"We also need to do the hospital
OL,15,Fmodernisation which will then give us
OL,16,Faccess to another four more theatres,
OL,17,Fagain, very important with regard to
OL,18,Forthopaedics."
